<br>
Need to get a map and find out what locations the ports are and what route to avoid any dangers to that city.<br>
<br>
Thanks again.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/utangting.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TangTing</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 94<br> <font color=#333333>(10/19/02 1:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1602.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Katta</span><hr size=1> I don't think Katta has any more of the lvl 24 pet scrolls than you can purchase at the guild in Freeport, Qeynos, etc(if it even has those).  Katta definitely has lvl 39 air, water, and fire scrolls and all lvl 44 pets.  If you zone to the top level of the twilight sea tower from fungus grove, once you go down the stairs there is a merchant who sells many of the components needed for the lvl 24 water and fire pet scrolls (I think).  If you go the route from Nexus to Echo Caverns to Fungus Grove to Twilight Sea make sure you are invis at all times. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/utangting.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TangTing</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 95<br> <font color=#333333>(10/19/02 1:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1602.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Katta</span><hr size=1> But if Katta does have the water and fire lvl 24 scrolls thats important info. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uusrbinperldashw.showPublicProfile?language=EN>usrbinperl dashw</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 263<br> <font color=#333333>(10/19/02 7:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1602.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.attbi.com/~chort/images/doin-tux.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Katta</span><hr size=1> 1.) Erudite will be fine in Katta, as long as you don't worship and Evil deity<br>
2.) I'm pretty sure that vendor doesn't sell lvl 24 pets.<br>
<br>
