<br>
When you get to KC, look for a building that has a huge bush surrounding the building, the building on the left of it is the Mag, Wizzie, Ench building. The one with some Dragon symbols on sides of the building. Go inside the building and walk around the back, you'll see a white square painting with a black dragon symbol in the middle. That painting is clickable. Click on said painting 3 times and you're at the 3rd floor where you need to be.<br>
Then go to your right back corner from where you were facing the painting and the Mag room is there.<br>
In fact they're all in the same corner on each floor except for the top floor.<br>
<br>
The first and second floor does nothing and does not respond to hails, so I surmise they are quest Mags or will be later on if they're put there for future use. Or possibly for new future spells, PoP possibly?<br>
<br>
I'm non KoS as a Erudite Mag, so any good race is safe to explore in KC.<br>
<br>
If you take a TL from a wizzie to the Twilight zone, here's the loc to get to the bridge to the KC zone.....Neg 400, Neg 1840.<br>
<br>
Be careful not to step into a nearby island next to the island where you will be TLed to. The surrounding mobs where you be TLed at are Mag pets. It's quite beautiful there and a haven for Mags <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
The island next to it is full of Shadowmen type mobs. They're red to me at lvl 29. Prolly safe for evil races I think. Not sure tho.<br>
<br>
KC seems to be a pretty cool zone. Except there are some thieves wander around that will jump you at the far right side of the zone and there's a graveyard there too where the undead will spawn from the ground and attack you. (Read that from eqatlas.com). So I didn't bother to check and see what they con from there and I'm not going to. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
The zone is always dark, so summon a heatstone or coldstone, those will help alot.<br>
<br>
Some peeps there hunt the guards for exp. I have no plans to hunt the guards for exp since I rather keep good faction with all good cities.<br>
<br>
Those with evil races such as the DEs, if you plan to kill the guards for exp, wait until AFTER you got your lvl 44 pet spells from KC. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
That is all.<br>
